pageContent: Purpose: We evaluated the efficacy and safety of hyperbaric oxygenation therapy to preserve erectile function as part of penile rehabilitation after robot assisted bilateral nerve sparing radical prostatectomy for prostate cancer.

metaData.source:
Prospective evaluation of early postoperative male and female sexual function after radical prostatectomy with erectile nerves preservation
https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25588959/
